{"type": "article", "id": 6972, "title": "The Goldfish Tea Bag 小金鱼茶包", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-02T07:39:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060523414559fDrAF6HOWTwRgM.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t茶包存在已久，但只有台湾人把它们做成了小金鱼的形状。这家名为 Charm Villa 遵循着“设计有趣的产品”这个原则，把茶包做成小金鱼的样子。当茶包泡在水中，放佛一只小金鱼在水里游来游去。简单自然，一下子让我们此刻的时候充满了乐趣。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234144XueVhzpL7KMrQ5iB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"1.41388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234144hpcBugke0H3wAlZR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"1.41388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}